wlauto/external/revent

added feature:
1. linear scaling and shift.
2. translate events to type B with mtdev.
   (http://www.linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/svn/general/mtdev.html)
3. replay events on assigned input device.
4. add a type B virutal device.
